cleaned_text: Fine Balance Acupuncture Consultorios médicos Sobre nosotros Fine Balance Acupuncture is committed to helping you find optimal health and well-being. According to Oriental Medicine, optimal health is a balance of yin and yang. Too much of one or not enough of the other can lead to disharmonies that affect the health of our body, mind & spirit. Balance in this sense is not stationary like weights on a balanced scale, but rather it is a changing state. When the forces of yin and yang within us are balanced there is equilibrium internally and we feel healthy.
